ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Repealing paragraph (a) of Order in Council P.C. 2013-1354 of December 9, 2013
PrecisOrder Repealing paragraph (a) of Order in Council P.C. 2013-1354 of December 9, 2013, as a result of this repeal, the collective bargaining process in place before the 2013 Order was implemented would be restored; however, Treasury Board approval of the terms and conditions of employment for non-unionized employees would be maintained.
